HEADWORD: Wayz-goose
<hw>Wayz"-goose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Wase</ets>
stubble + <ets>goose</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A stubble goose.</def> <mark>[Obs. or Prov.
