[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An annual feast of the persons employed in a
printing office.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>way-goose</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

